summary: I got to see Detective Pikachu last night!!! It was so good, I loved looking for all of the Pokemon in the background and seeing...
body:
I got to see Detective Pikachu last night!!! It was so good, I loved looking for all of the Pokemon in the background and seeing who was there. And honestly? I love how they all looked! Sure some looked weird or creepy but it worked for what they were!

Now I’ve been thinking about what my partner Pokemon would be, and all I know is I would want something fluffy.

summary:
My Mum, asking me what all the different Pokémon were called after watching Detective Pikachu: 
“What was that... licky......
body:
My Mum, asking me what all the different Pokémon were called after watching Detective Pikachu:

“What was that… licky… tongue Pokémon?”

Me:

“That’s Lickitung.”
